{"PALO":[{"def":"A pole or timber of any kind; -- in the names of trees.","pos":""}],"PALOLA":[{"def":"An annelid (Palola viridis) which, at certain seasons of the year, swarms at the surface of the sea about some of the Pcific Islands, where it is collected for food.","pos":""},{"def":"A polystome worm (Palolo viridis) that burrows in the coral reefs of certain of the Pacific Islands.","pos":""}]}